# service_contexts — maps named Binder services to SELinux labels.
#
# potvolumed does NOT register any Binder service of its own.
# It is a pure client: it calls AudioSystem (AudioPolicyService) but
# never calls AServiceManager_addService().
#
# This file is intentionally empty (no service registrations).
# It is included here so the build system finds the expected file in the
# sepolicy/private/ directory without producing a "file not found" warning.
